<h1 id="create-an-interest-code-with-a-range" sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Create an interest code with a range</h1>


<p sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="31">Interest codes can be set up to calculate different interest amounts based on a range of values. This procedure will show you how to add an interest code and add a range to it.</p>
<ol sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Go to Credit and collections &gt; Interest &gt; Set up interest codes.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="35">In the Interest code field, enter the name of the interest code.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">In the Description field, enter a description for the interest code.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="37">Select Month.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Expand the Earnings section.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Expand the Earnings by currency section.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">In the Ledger posting account field, specify the desired values.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">In the Interest by range field, select 'Months'.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Click Add.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">In the Description field, enter a description for this currency and range.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Click Save.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Click Ranges.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Enter the From value as 0 and then enter the interest percent per month that will be used to calculate the interest. For our example, it is 1.5.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">Enter the next From value as 4, which is the first month that you will be calculating a new interest amount.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Enter the interest percent per month that will be used to calculate the interest starting in month 4. For this example, it is 2.0.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Enter the next From value as 7, which is the next month that you will be calculating a new interest amount.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">Enter the interest percent per month that will be used to calculate the interest starting in month 7. For this example, it is 2.5.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-interest-code-range.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Click Close to complete the setup.</li>
</ol>
